org.openimaj.util.iterator

Class TextLineIterable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.util.iterator.TextLineIterable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>

    public class TextLineIterable
extends Object
implements Iterable<String>
    An Iterable that can provide access to lines of a text file referenced by a File or URL. It is safe to re-use this Iterable instance; a new BufferedReader will be created when iterator() is called. Any IOExceptions are wrapped as RuntimeExceptions.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
